VALUES (644, NULL, 236, 582,
        '<p>You can use&nbsp;VechainThor wallet and get dividend from your holdings, but i recommend to use hardware wallet like trezor or ledger. It gives you maximum security of your funds. If you trade short term you can also keep your funds on crypticurrency exchange like Binance or KuCoin.</p>\r\n',
