VALUES (664, NULL, 235, 606,
        '<p>I recommend to use just a bitcoin exchange office. This is the fastest option, which does not even require verification. Of course it depends how much bitcoin you want to buy. If it is more than a few hundred dollar, I recommend setting up an account on the binance. You can pay there with a debit card with very low commission. The binance exchange allows for a lot of trading options. It has probably the most currency pairs on the market. Recently, they also invest in DeFi market. I think you should learn about decentralized finances if you want to make good, quick income! Good luck bro!</p>\r\n',
