VALUES (1771, 234, '2020-10-28 16:23:13', '2020-10-28 16:23:13', 1,
        '{\"message\":{\"content\":649,\"type_id\":2,\"title\":\"What is your investment strategy?\",\"reason\":1,\"comment_id\":768,\"description\":\"<p>I simply invest on a long-term basis. I never invest more than I can lose and I only put in the market the money that I won&#39;t need in the nearest future in my daily life.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>I also invest mainly in assets I believe in, such as Bitcoin. I strongly believe in the development of blockchain technology and that is why even when the price of bitcoin has a strong turmoil, I know that I will not lose and sooner or later I will gain profit. I also invest in gold and physical silver.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}',
