VALUES (1772, 234, '2020-10-28 16:24:05', '2020-10-28 16:24:05', 1,
        '{\"message\":{\"content\":648,\"type_id\":2,\"title\":\"What cryptocurrency debit card?\",\"reason\":1,\"comment_id\":769,\"description\":\"<p>Hello. I heard about Wirex some time ago, people&#39;s opinions were divided. Some are satisfied and others complain about high commissions and small selection of coins. I, for my part, recommend Crypto.com cards or coinbase cards. Both cards have a good reputation from users and positive opinions. Also it&#39;s good thing to keep privacy and anonimity.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}',
