VALUES (1809, 238, '2020-10-31 17:15:03', '2020-10-31 17:15:03', 1,
        '{\"message\":{\"content\":646,\"type_id\":2,\"title\":\"How to create a paper wallet?\",\"reason\":1,\"comment_id\":781,\"description\":\"<p>Creating a paper wallet shouldn&#39;t be very difficult for anyone, it&#39;s enough to get well involved in the process and after some time they will be interested in becoming owners of the above mentioned tools.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>First of all, people should have a good look at their operating system, whether it is free of harmful viruses. Then you need to download some files, such as a paper wallet generation script called GitHub. The downloaded files should be unpacked on your computer and one of the most important elements is to disconnect your computer from the Internet so that everything can be done 100% safely.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>A convenient option created for all interested people is the so-called paper wallet generator. Just run it on your computer after downloading the above mentioned files. The generator will guide the person through the whole wallet creation process until a satisfactory result is obtained.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}',
        781, 235, 5, 6, 0, 'en_US');
INSERT INTO `notices`
VALUES (1810, 235, '2020-10-31 17:17:09', '2020-10-31 17:17:09', 1,
        '{\"message\":{\"content\":665,\"type_id\":2,\"title\":\"Property flipping - is it worth?\",\"reason\":1,\"comment_id\":782,\"description\":\"<p>Each investment is different, and each of us has different possibilities. Depending on different factors, investors earn from 10 to 40 thousand dollars on one flip. It happens, of course, that we underestimate the cost of renovation or the sale will be prolonged and on one investment we will earn &quot;only&quot; 5 thousand, but on another we can earn even 50 thousand. As a matter of assurance, we can assume that on average we earn 20 thousand on a flip, although for experienced investors it is rather the minimum rate for one flip.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If our resources (or creditworthiness) allows us to invest in one flip apartment, we will earn on average 80 thousand dolar per year. One investment should not last longer than 3 months.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can also treat flipping as an additional source of income and make one such investment per year. However, i am convinced that once you invest in real estate, house flipping will become your main source of income.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}',
        782, 239, 5, 6, 0, 'en_US');
INSERT INTO `notices`
VALUES (1811, 238, '2020-10-31 17:18:43', '2020-10-31 17:18:43', 1,
        '{\"message\":{\"content\":663,\"type_id\":2,\"title\":\"Trezor and Ledger - what\'s the difference?\",\"reason\":1,\"comment_id\":783,\"description\":\"<p>The question of wallet selection depends on the client&#39;s specific preferences. Trezors are considered reliable, moreover, you can store Cardano on them. Other wallets do not offer this possibility, which may be of benefit to Trezor. However, his disadvantage is the high price compared to Ledger.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Production costs and quality as well as longer history of the company make Trezor costs even 100% more than Ledger. Ledger&#39;s advantage is that as a relatively new company he has to enter the market and win customers. The products made by the entrepreneurs are of good quality and cheaper than the competitors&#39; equipment. The choice between two wallets is difficult, because each of them is relatively good. &nbsp;The bigger problem is to determine which wallet you want to choose at all. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}',
        783, 239, 5, 6, 0, 'en_US');
