VALUES (2097, 230, '2021-01-11 19:07:38', '2021-01-11 19:07:38', 1,
        '{\"message\":{\"content\":737,\"type_id\":2,\"title\":\"How to migrate liquidity from Uniswap to Sushiswap?\",\"reason\":1,\"comment_id\":847,\"description\":\"<p>You can migrate your LP tokens with a few simple steps. On the sushi official website go to SushiswapFi. Once you unlock your wallet on right hand side information will pop-up &ldquo;Migrate for better rewards&rdquo;. When you click-it then a new window will appear and show all your Uniswap Liquidity polls available. Simply just choose the liquidity pool you want to migrate. Type in the amount of LP tokens and confirm it. Then click &ldquo;confirm&rdquo; the transaction on the confirmation screen in your wallet application. Wait for it to be mined. And that is it all done. Always remember you have to pay a gas fee on Ethereum network so you need to have some Eth balance in your wallet. Remember that all your profit is calculated from the trades made on the pairs that you provided so it all depends where people trade more&nbsp;SushiSwap or Uniswap.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}',
        847, 228, 5, 6, 0, 'en_US');
